| comment "Dragnet [Ransomware]: dragnet-ransomware-2024-4423 — Recovery Inhibition (raworld)"
| comment "Status: experimental | Level: high | ID: bc12e16b-f6e2-55c7-9ee5-57d2652c31e3"
